                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within 30 feet of the sun-spire begins to Cast a Spell that has the fire or light trait</p><hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The sun-spire attempts to redirect the energy from the triggering effect into its sunlight stores. The sun-spire attempts to counteract the triggering spell with a [[/r {1d20+22} #counteract]]{+22} counteract bonus. If it successfully counteracts the spell, the sun-spire's sunlight stores are empowered. While empowered, the sun-spire deals an additional [[/r {2d8}[fire]]]{2d8 fire damage} with all of its attacks and abilities. The sun-spire remains empowered until the end of its next turn.</p>"
                },
                "requirements": {
                    "value": ""
                },
                "rules": [
                    {
                        "domain": "damage-roll",
                        "key": "RollOption",
